Document: Label3D
Path: godot/classes/class_label3d.rst
Summary: Describes methods for generating a triangle mesh from a Label3D and managing its draw flags.

Method: generate_triangle_mesh() -> TriangleMesh
Returns a TriangleMesh with the label's vertices following its current configuration (such as its pixel_size).

Method: get_draw_flag(flag: DrawFlags) -> bool
Returns the value of the specified flag.

Method: set_draw_flag(flag: DrawFlags, enabled: bool) -> void
If `true`, the specified `flag` will be enabled.